{"3301670": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "My Goth Goblin Princess", "steam_appid": 3301670, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301670/extras/582c0757ac1cba26b3b379eaa62b0b90.poster.avif?t=1772021829\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301670/extras/582c0757ac1cba26b3b379eaa62b0b90.webm?t=1772021829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301670/extras/582c0757ac1cba26b3b379eaa62b0b90.mp4?t=1772021829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301670/extras/ddc23f5973c3df810fca4d574a9483eb.avif?t=1772021829\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a humiliating defeat, you've been brought to the goblin kingdom as a prisoner. Instead of ending your life, the goblin queen decides to offer you as a gift to her daughter. This will be her undoing as you and the goblin princess plot together to unleash her magic powers through intense mystical training, and overtake the goblin kingdom's throne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301670/extras/1879362b3cda1e546d7b4496e952cbde.poster.avif?t=1772021829\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301670/extras/1879362b3cda1e546d7b4496e952cbde.webm?t=1772021829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste